OMNICHANNEL PAYMENT SOLUTIONS 
                            Global solutions for your business payment needs. Global Payments is focused on delivering innovative payment technology solutions to help your business succeed and focus on what you do best.
                        

 

                Learn More
            











ONLINE SOLUTIONS 
                            Ecommerce payment features that are designed with your business in mind. Our global solutions make it quick and easy for you to accept transactions.
                        

 

                Learn More
            











CROSS-BORDER 
                            Integrating cutting-edge ideas on a global scale – our worldwide presence offers payment technology solutions to multinational companies. Our global footprint in international markets all around the world can assist your growing business.
                        

 

                Learn More
            











INTEGRATED SOLUTIONS 
                            Use our innovative integrated solutions to streamline your business operations. Payments technology integrated into your software can make your solutions more valuable to the businesses using them.
                        

 

                Learn More
            











MOBILE 
                            Dynamic mobile payment solutions for your customers on the go. Our technology platform provides you all the tools that you would need to accept payments on your phone.
                        

 

                Learn More
            






 




Service. Driven. Commerce 
                        We are committed to exemplary Service to our employees, customers and communities. Driven by passion to innovate, we meet the needs of our customers. As payment technology experts, we bring our expertise and global perspective to Commerce.
                    















President and Chairman of ETA 2017 and Global Payments’ CEO Jeff Sloan, talks about the worldwide scope of ETA and the future of payment technology.
 


Read about the technology and trends that shape the evolution of the payments technology industry.












Millennials and Mobile Payments: The Way Forward

With approximately 80 million millennials in the United States alone and with their increased usage of smartphones, the world is literally at the tips of their fingers. How are millennials shaping the future of digital and mobile payments?

Continue Reading
 
The Transformation of the Payments Industry: How Revolutionary Technology Has Changed the Way We Pay
Over the past few decades, the payments industry has gone through significant changes. To understand this journey and what lies ahead, we will take a look at some of the key breakthroughs that have had a major impact on the world and the innovations that continue to revolutionize the payments industry.

Continue Reading











