Giving Back Globally Corporate Citizenship 


As a Service. Driven. Commerce company, Global Payments does its utmost to be a responsible corporate citizen and our employees demonstrate passion and enthusiasm for making a difference in the lives of others. As a member of the global business community, our corporate citizenship is fundamental to our company values and who we are, and we take action around the world to create change by offering our time, services and financial assistance to those in need.


 

