Global Markets
Global Payments has spent over 50 years in the merchant processing and acquiring business, accumulating significant experience and technological knowledge. Merchant acquiring and processing for both debit and credit cards is our primary business. Global Payments has been a leader in the U.S. market since the 1960s, when its former parent company, National Data Corporation, pioneered electronic payment processing.
Headquartered in Atlanta, Georgia with 8,500 employees worldwide, Global Payments is a Fortune 1000 Company with merchants and partners in 30 countries throughout North America, Europe, the Asia-Pacific region and Brazil. 









We Make Winning a Habit 
We’re committed to excellence in our products and services which makes it critical for us to recruit resourceful, empowered and talented employees. If you can see yourself in this kind of company, we invite you to apply.


 

